social_posts.post_text:
I’m so excited to share my new work for the @fourseasons 🥂 I had so much fun filming this project!! 
directed by the amazing @shawnmerz 
produced by @chrome.productions ✨ @margauxtheagency 

“When @fourseasons asked us to capture the newly refreshed @beverlywilshire right in our backyard, we knew that we had to find the right storyline. The legendary hotel at the end of Rodeo Drive is an absolute icon and @Chrome.Productions was delighted to have the opportunity to capture its magic. Our film follows a pair of guests as their paths cross repeatedly in the property's various culinary experiences, luxuriously redesigned rooms and even the picture perfect elevator - all to show at the end of the day, luxury is what you make of it.” - @chrome.productions
